.SS dev
.sp
Deploying the ceph\-installer HTTP service to a remote server with ansible.
This command wraps ansible and certain flags to make it easier to deploy
a development version.
.sp
Usage:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
ceph\-installer dev $HOST
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
